## User Test Feedback

### General
- Add close icon (x) to popup windows
- Support screen sizes just below hd (1920x1080) like hd-ready (1366x768)
- Add hover over explanation to fields inside formulas like "Raise Alarm"
- Disable drop-down fields if they hold no data
- Alarms = incidents? Incidents are more describing than alarms
- Data tables should not have ordering in the button columns (like edit alarm col in alarm overview)
- Mandatory formula fields should be more clear (add '*' for example)
- JS heavy operations eat the pc resources (Anders pc could not handle the frontend?)

### Getting Started
- Demo data should show all most used logs (conn, dns, http etc.) instead of just the suricata
- Fewer choices/scenarios in getting started (makes it easier to startup)

### Analysis tool
- Move the info points just above the analysis table, col value make the table jump.
- Make the info points above the analysis table more clear, Anders didn't see them at first
- Scroll bars (or similar) to the data analysis table, maybe mouse scroll
- More clear indication that the analysis table is moving (scrolling)
- Hidden fields confusing (remove col entirely?)
- Filter free text needs more explaining (log point filter language)
- Filter free text needs more wildcards synonyms
- Filter free text should be more forgiving (more text alternatives to the and, not and so on, perhaps add the logical operators)
- Add filter buttons to the analysis tool (like we used to). They relied more on the gui than the hotkeys (could be enabled or disabled)
- Filter active icon should be flipped (show current state)
- It should be more clear when a filter is active, when written in the filter field (maybe add a filter tab to the list like with temp filters?)
- Temp filters name should include some of the filter instead (easier to differentiate?)
- Analysis tool should be more forgiving about the empty field
- Make it more clear that the plus icon in log tabs can add new tabs (somehow?)
- Hide popup does not disable hotkeys (bug)
- Double click on row should open popup with additional info (like col value, whois?)
- Double click should make a filter out of the clicked field

### Alarm Overview
- Show data should open a new tab with data instead of redirect (easier to go back to alarm overview)
- Edit Alarm popup says "Edit alarm status" (button and popup headline should say the same)
- Alarm info should show all data (drop show expert data button?)
- Alarm notes should not close the immediately popup after a new note is added, instead tell the user that a note has been added.
- Add new alarm notes by using enter button besides the button
- Alarm overview timeraised don't show minutes and seconds (bug)

### Raise Alarm
- Add more data to manual alarm instead of just one data point
- Alarm types are not clear (add examples, prefill? change to select?)
- Close tab after an alarm has been manually raised
- Is the alarm note field needed on the raise alarm page?

### Sensor overview
- Delete sensor should warn that alarms are also deleted (add documentation)

## Suggestions
- Use HotJar to track user movement (maybe too invasive)
- Two different front ends, one for experts another for ordinary users
- Analysis tool looks a bit like wireshark, should follow the same logic.
- Extrahop has really nice GUI, maybe book a demo and be "inspired".
- Pentest your system (felix and friends? open hunt?)
